snippet.title: LIMINALCORE REVEAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
*Official First Trailer for Liminalcore - In game footage*
Follow us on:
🔹Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/3107900/Liminalcore/
🔹Discord : https://discord.gg/RByXUSMPpG
🔹X: https://x.com/ShadowOwlStudio?s=09

*A psychological horror exploration game that emphasizes the eerie atmosphere of liminal spaces over monster chases or jump scares.*
